Title: Series: Galerie Leuchtenberg
Description: Plate 85: Rest on the flight into Egypt, after Cantarini, with St Joseph handing some dates to Christ Child, who lies on the Virgin's lap; two angels are seen pulling the tree's leaves at top right; in outline Etching
Curator's comments: For comment on series see 1851,1213.322. Engraved after a copy or a replica of a painting which is now in the Pinacoteca di Brera, Milan; see Mancigotti, 'Simone Cantarini', 1975, p.110.
